data.text:
Meaghan Brander, our Film Industry Growth Specialist, was recently featured in a profile in The Buzz! Meagan is developing a film strategy for PEI which has two important components: to attract non-Island investors and productions, and to work with FilmPEI to grow local talent. Learn more about Meaghan in the article here: https://bit.ly/3qn0Idb
